@NODE "Asked Questions"

@{b}Q:@{ub} ButtonBar opens on frontmost screen, which I don't like.
@{b}A:@{ub} In menu @{i}Properties/Booleans@{ui} mark @{i}Open on Wb@{ui} box to force
   opening on Workbench.

   If you can code opening on any screen by screen's pubname (not it's title!)
   in Blitz, I can incorporate this, but now ...
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@{b}Q:@{ub} I want ButtonBar to hide all columns once I click outside it.
@{b}A:@{ub} In menu @{i}Properties/Booleans@{ui} set @{i}Column mode@{ui} to
   @{i}Autoclose@{ui}

@ENDNODE
